# Gracelyn University — Ambassador Scaling Program
# Copy to a secure location and set these in the Catalyst Console
# (Configurations -> Environment Variables). DO NOT commit a filled-in .env.
# These are SECRETS. Never paste real values into the repo, issues, or PRs.
