# Canonical names only. Aliases found in the design docs (CLAUDE_API_KEY,
# OPENAI_ASSISTANT_ID, HEYGEN_AVATAR_ID, META_ACCESS_TOKEN) are intentionally
# NOT used. Ad spend is split per-platform (META_/GOOGLE_DAILY_SPEND_THRESHOLD).
